Herman Mashaba suspended ombudsman S'duduzo Gumede, an advocate, following a closed council meeting. CAPE TOWN Johannesburg Mayor Herman Mashaba suspended Ombudsman S'duduzo Gumede following a recent closed meeting.Mashaba says that problems started when the ombudsman s office was established.In an interview with 702 s Xolani Gwala, Mashaba explains why he suspended Gumede.Listen to the audio below for more details.(Edited by Shimoney Regter)